de: Annex B - Framework Agreement between the Swiss Contribution, acting through the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs of Switzerland and UNCTAD, ITC, UNIDO, ILO and UNOPS on the Implementation of Interagency Trade-Related Assistance in selected LDCS  - 07-12-2011 - Vereinbarung zwischen der Schweiz, vertreten durch das SECO, und dem Büro der Vereinten Nationen für Projektdienste (UNOPS) betreffend die Schaffung eines Treuhandfonds zur Finanzierung eines technischen Assistenzprojektes in Tansania
en: Annex B - Framework Agreement between the Swiss Contribution, acting through the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs of Switzerland and UNCTAD, ITC, UNIDO, ILO and UNOPS on the Implementation of Interagency Trade-Related Assistance in selected LDCS  - 07-12-2011 - Contribution Agreement between the United Nations Office for Project Services (UNOPS) and the Government of the Swiss Confederation, represented by the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs of Switzerland (seco) concerning United Nations Trade Cluster Programme Tanzania
fr: Annex B - Framework Agreement between the Swiss Contribution, acting through the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs of Switzerland and UNCTAD, ITC, UNIDO, ILO and UNOPS on the Implementation of Interagency Trade-Related Assistance in selected LDCS  - 07-12-2011 - Accord entre la Suisse, représentée par le SECO, et le Bureau des Nations Unies des services d'appui aux projets (UNOPS) concernant l'établissement d'un fonds pour le financement d'un programme de coopération technique en Tanzanie
